OL,3,CKlopp opens Instagram account to stay
OL,4,Cin touch with Liverpool fans
OL,6,FLiverpool FC's outgoing manager has
OL,7,Fopened an to keep in touch with fans.
OL,9,Fafter nine seasons in charge at
OL,10,FAnfield.
OL,12,FIn his first verified post, he shared
OL,13,Fa video saying: "Leaving this
OL,14,Fincredible place is hard.
OL,16,F"But I want to stay in contact with
OL,17,Fyou and even when I'm not a social
OL,18,Fmedia guy people told me social media
OL,19,Fhelps with that. So here we go."
