OL,3,CKlopp opens Instagram account to stay
OL,4,Cin touch with Liverpool fans
OL,6,FIt has been a week of goodbyes for
OL,7,FKlopp.
OL,9,FOn Saturday, the Liverpool Echo
OL,10,Fpublished in which he professed his
OL,11,Flove of the city and its people.
OL,13,FHe wrote: "For me, Liverpool is the
OL,14,Fcity of open arms. A place that
OL,15,Fwelcomes you like a son and does not
OL,16,Fcare where you come from.
OL,18,F"It just wants you to be part of it
OL,19,Fand I could not be prouder that you
OL,20,Fallowed me to have that incredible
OL,21,Fprivilege."
