OL,3,CKlopp opens Instagram account to stay
OL,4,Cin touch with Liverpool fans
OL,6,FKlopp has called for the final game of
OL,7,Fthe season, against Wolves, hoping to
OL,8,Fkeep emotional goodbye to as 'normal'
OL,9,Fas possible.
OL,11,FAs far back as 2017, Klopp told
OL,12,Findependent LFC website that he was
OL,13,F"definitely too old for social media".
OL,15,FHowever, he later revealed to
OL,16,FtalkSPORT that he did have a private
OL,17,FInstagram account for keeping tabs on
OL,18,Fbirthdays and what his squad had been
OL,19,Fgetting up to away from training.
