OL,3,CKlopp opens Instagram account to stay
OL,4,Cin touch with Liverpool fans
OL,6,FHis new verified account, based in
OL,7,FGermany and opened in April, has
OL,8,Falready attracted hundreds of
OL,9,Fthousands of followers since the video
OL,10,Fwas published on Saturday morning.
OL,12,FKlopp told fans: "I've wondered always
OL,13,Fwhat it feels like when we write a
OL,14,Fstory together and that's how it feels
OL,15,Flike today.
OL,17,F"It's a good book and if we read it in
OL,18,Fthe future we will have a smile on our
OL,19,Fface."
